name: Verboten
description:
2615 x 3300 pixels virtual representation of the 22 x 27.5 cm artwork "Verboten" (edition of 1).

The owner of this NFT has the right to swap the physical artwork for this NFT, and must whenever receiving the physical artwork immediately send this NFT to the other party.

The physical artwork has this NFT's address written at the back of it.
